ouchdown-@-2000-x-1270-Darren-Gerrish_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/teezo-touchdown-@-2000-x-1270-Darren-Gerrish_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/teezo-touchdown-@-2000-x-1270-Darren-Gerrish_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/teezo-touchdown-@-2000-x-1270-Darren-Gerrish_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/teezo-touchdown-@-2000-x-1270-Darren-Gerrish_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/teezo-touchdown-@-2000-x-1270-Darren-Gerrish_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/teezo-touchdown">Teezo Touchdown</a>分享了他对<a href="/artists/kendrick-lamar">Kendrick Lamar</a>在他臭名昭著的<a href="/artists/drake">Drake</a> diss 歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-tells-drake-i-hear-you-like-em-young-on-fresh-diss-track-not-like-us-3753559">“Not Like Us</a> ”中点名他的想法。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/drake-and-kendrick-lamars-feud-the-full-timeline-3754820">德雷克和肯德里克·拉马尔的不和：完整的时间表</a></li></ul><p>早在四月份， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/drake-and-kendrick-lamars-feud-the-full-timeline-3754820">德雷克和拉马尔就发生了一场备受瞩目的争执</a>，他们互相发表激烈的 diss 曲目。 Lamar 发送的最后一首歌曲是《Not Like Us》，它成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tiktok-unveil-songs-of-the-summer-2024-3784965">TikTok 的夏日歌曲</a>之一， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamars-drake-diss-not-like-us-breaks-records-billboard-number-one-3756060">登上<em>Billboard</em> Hot 100 榜首</a>，并成为 Spotify 上单日播放量最多的嘻哈歌曲。</p><p>在《不像我们》中，拉马尔说唱道： <em>“男人下来，呼叫琥珀灯，告诉他，‘呼吸，兄弟’/把一个黑鬼钉在十字架上，他像蒂佐一样四处走动”</em> </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="不像我们" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/T6eK-2OQtew?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在接受<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/rb-hip-hop/teezo-touchdown-2024-rb-hip-hop-rookie-of-the-year-1235767187/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Billboard</em></a>采访时，Touchdown 评论了拉马尔点名他的事情，透露他当时正处于自己的“泡沫”中，直到后来才知道这位康普顿说唱歌手这样做了。然而，他坚称自己是中立的，并很荣幸能与两位说唱歌手进行同样的对话。</p><p> “我决定不再听取任何来来回回的意见，”他透露道。 “我看到了一种暴民心态，我不喜欢分裂。抱歉，我太笨了，但这里充满了爱。 [简单的事实是他们都]知道我是谁……这仍然是你必须掐自己的时刻之一。博蒙特的那个孩子，我很确定他现在正在从屋顶上跳下去。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_jQlUlOLrO/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,