s-3773722">，他的附属机构、记者和媒体名人 DJ Akademiks 表示，6God 目前正在创作新音乐</a>。</p><p>几位备受瞩目的说唱传奇人物对德雷克与拉马尔的冲突发表了评论： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/andre-3000-says-the-kendrick-drake-feud-made-him-a-little-sad-3782642">安德烈 3000 表示这让他感到“有点悲伤”，</a>而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/questlove-criticises-drake-and-kendrick-lamar-for-mudslinging-in-rap-beef-3754711">奎斯特洛夫则称这种争执是“摔跤比赛级别的诽谤和不择手段的打倒”</a> 。</p><p>最近，《Not Like Us》的制作人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mustard">Mustard</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mustard-calls-drake-a-strange-guy-following-kendrick-lamar-feud-3787085">将 Drake 称为“奇怪的人”</a> ，而亿万富翁<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/michael-rubin-banned-not-like-us-at-his-annual-white-party-for-drake-it-was-the-appropriate-thing-3784133">Michael Rubin 禁止在今年的年度聚会上使用这首歌，</a>因为 OVO 创始人出席了。</p><p>在其他新闻中，Touchdown 为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/every-song-despicable-me-4-soundtrack-3774015">《<em>卑鄙的我 4</em> 》原声带创作了大胆的流行朋克歌曲“None Of Your Business”。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/teezo-touchdown-responds-to-kendrick-lamar-namedropping-him-on-not-like-us-3791257">Teezo Touchdown 的帖子对 Kendrick Lamar 在《Not Like Us》中点名他的回应</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
波普艺术先驱、大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie) 和 The Clash 合作者德里克·博希尔 (Derek Boshier) 去世，享年 87 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/pop-art-pioneer-and-david-bowie-and-the-clash-collaborator-derek-boshier-dies-age-87-3791447?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=流行艺术先锋和大卫·鲍伊和冲突合作者德里克·博什尔·迪斯-87Anagricel Duran Fri, 06 Sep 2024 17:45:00 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3791447 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-and-his-artwork-for-David-Bowies-Lodger-album.-Credit-Aaron-Davidson-via-Getty-and-PRESS.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="德里克·博希尔 (Derek Boshier) 和他为大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie) 的《Lodger》专辑创作的艺术作品。图片来源：Aaron Davidson，来自 Getty 和 PRESS" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-and-his-artwork-for-David-Bowies-Lodger-album.-Credit-Aaron-Davidson-via-Getty-and-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-and-his-artwork-for-David-Bowies-Lodger-album.-Credit-Aaron-Davidson-via-Getty-and-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-and-his-artwork-for-David-Bowies-Lodger-album.-Credit-Aaron-Davidson-via-Getty-and-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-and-his-artwork-for-David-Bowies-Lodger-album.-Credit-Aaron-Davidson-via-Getty-and-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-and-his-artwork-for-David-Bowies-Lodger-album.-Credit-Aaron-Davidson-via-Getty-and-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-and-his-artwork-for-David-Bowies-Lodger-album.-Credit-Aaron-Davidson-via-Getty-and-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位艺术家在洛杉矶的家中安详去世</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pop-art-pioneer-and-david-bowie-and-the-clash-collaborator-derek-boshier-dies-age-87-3791447">后波普艺术先驱、David Bowie 和 The Clash 合作者 Derek Boshier 去世，享年 87 岁，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-and-his-artwork-for-David-Bowies-Lodger-album.-Credit-Aaron-Davidson-via-Getty-and-PRESS.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="德里克·博希尔 (Derek Boshier) 和他为大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie) 的《Lodger》专辑创作的艺术作品。图片来源：Aaron Davidson，来自 Getty 和 PRESS" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-and-his-artwork-for-David-Bowies-Lodger-album.-Credit-Aaron-Davidson-via-Getty-and-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-and-his-artwork-for-David-Bowies-Lodger-album.-Credit-Aaron-Davidson-via-Getty-and-PRESS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-and-his-artwork-for-David-Bowies-Lodger-album.-Credit-Aaron-Davidson-via-Getty-and-PRESS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-and-his-artwork-for-David-Bowies-Lodger-album.-Credit-Aaron-Davidson-via-Getty-and-PRESS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-and-his-artwork-for-David-Bowies-Lodger-album.-Credit-Aaron-Davidson-via-Getty-and-PRESS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-and-his-artwork-for-David-Bowies-Lodger-album.-Credit-Aaron-Davidson-via-Getty-and-PRESS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>因与<a href="/artists/David-Bowie">David Bowie</a>和<a href="/artists/The-Clash">The Clash</a>等人合作而闻名的英国波普艺术先驱 Derek Boshier 去世，享年 87 岁。</p><p>这位出生于朴茨茅斯的艺术家以其在英国波普艺术界的作品而闻名，并从自己的工人阶级根源中获得了自豪和灵感。他的公关 Daniel Bee 今天（9 月 6 日）证实了他的去世，他告诉<em>PA Media</em> （通过<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/music/article/2024/sep/06/british-pop-art-pioneer-derek-boshier-dies-david-bowie-clash" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报</em></a>》），这位艺术家在洛杉矶的家中安详地去世。</p><p> “毫无疑问，德里克·博希尔帮助创建和定义了伦敦和美国的波普艺术运动，”比说。 “他对过去 60 年来流行文化的观察和评论在世界上最伟大的博物馆和画廊中清晰可见。我们将非常怀念他。” </p><figure id="attachment_3791471" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3791471" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3791471" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-posing.jpg" alt="Derek Boshier 于 2016 年 11 月 29 日在佛罗里达州迈阿密出席迈阿密艺术展 2016 VIP 预展。 （摄影：Aaron Davidson/Getty Images for Art Miami）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Derek-Boshier-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3791471" class="wp-caption-text"> Derek Boshier 于 2016 年 11 月 29 日在佛罗里达州迈阿密出席迈阿密艺术展 2016 VIP 预展。 （摄影：Aaron Davidson/Getty Images for Art Miami）</figcaption></figure><p> 1959 年至 1962 年间，博希尔就读于伦敦皇家艺术学院 (RCA)，并与艾伦·琼斯 (Allen Jones)、彼得·菲利普斯 (Peter Phillips) 和大卫·霍克尼 (David Hockney) 等其他有影响力的艺术家一起工作。</p><p>完成学业后，他继续在中央艺术与设计学院任教，他的学生之一是 The Clash 主唱 Joe Strummer。博希尔随后设计了乐队的第二本歌曲集，其中收录了艺术家的绘画作品。</p><p> 1979年，博什尔成功举办了一场题为“生活”的艺术展，他在展览中“选择了一系列艺术家的作品，其主题探讨了他人的生活”。该展览涵盖了广泛的艺术活动，从漫画家和平面设计师到视频和表演艺术家。一些知名人士包括霍克尼、RB Kitaj 和布鲁斯·麦克莱恩”（据<a href="https://www.serpentinegalleries.org/whats-on/lives-an-exhibition-of-artists-whose-work-is-based-on-other-peoples-lives/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">蛇形画廊</a>报道）。 </p><figure id="attachment_3791470" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3791470" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3791470" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Bowie-Billboard.jpg" alt="洛杉矶 - 1979 年：1979 年在洛杉矶为大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie) 专辑《Lodger》手绘的广告牌。 （图片来源：Getty Images）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Bowie-Billboard.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Bowie-Billboard-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Bowie-Billboard-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Bowie-Billboard-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Bowie-Billboard-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/David-Bowie-Billboard-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3791470" class="wp-caption-text">洛杉矶 – 1979 年：1979 年在洛杉矶为大卫·鲍伊 (David Bowie) 专辑《Lodger》手绘的广告牌。 （图片来源：Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>展览引起了鲍伊的注意，他要求博希尔进行介绍。从那时起，两人的友谊持续了三十多年，同年，波希尔为鲍伊的第十三张录音室专辑《Lodger》的设计做出了贡献。</p><p>据该艺术家的公关人员称，Boshier 是这位偶像 2016 年去世前手写便条的接收者之一。在这张便条上，这位《Let&#39;s Dance》歌手赞扬了 Boshier 当时的艺术书籍，鲍伊告诉 Boshier：他的作品“代代相传”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pop-art-pioneer-and-david-bowie-and-the-clash-collaborator-derek-boshier-dies-age-87-3791447">后波普艺术先驱、David Bowie 和 The Clash 合作者 Derek Boshier 去世，享年 87 岁，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
